      "role": "user",
      "content": "that makes sense. i'll try the counter approach first. but what if the leak isn't in this specific class? like what if it's some other object being created deep in the driver stack that i don't have direct visibility into? how do i hunt for those \"invisible\" allocations without the overhead of a full profiler?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
