    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "overriding new/delete sounds like a lot of work and might be too slow/risky for the production build. is there any other way to spot patterns? like, if it's a very slow leak, are there certain ways to tell if it's a single growing object or just thousands of tiny little bits of memory being lost everywhere?",
